---
import DocumentHead from '../layouts/DocumentHead.astro';
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

let title = `404 — You broke it | Garden of Thoughts`;
let permalink = 'https://sanketmaske.dev/404';


---

<html lang="en">
  <DocumentHead title={title} description="You broke it. Or we did. Probably you." permalink={permalink} />
  <body>
    <Layout page="">
      <div class="not-found">

        <span class="error-code">404</span>
        <span class="error-title">Oh wow!! You actually found nothing.</span>

        <div class="divider-full"></div>

        <p class="roast">
          Impressive. Out of all the pages that <em>do</em> exist on this site,
          you managed to navigate to one that doesn't. That takes talent.
        </p>

        <p class="roast">
          <strong>If you're a developer</strong> — you know what you did. That URL was wrong
          and you knew it before you hit enter. Admit it, you typed it just to see what happens.
          Congratulations, you found a 404.<br>
          Caught you!!!<br>
          The garden has real paths, real posts, and real content that won't throw errors at you. Use them. We're watching🙃
        </p>

        <p class="roast">
          <strong>If you're not a developer</strong> — first of all, hello! I completely
          trust you. This was clearly an accident and we don't judge accidents here.
          The garden is actually a lovely place when you're on the right path.
          Those cards below? They're your map. Pick one, click it, and pretend this
          never happened. I won't tell anyone. Promise.
        </p>

      
        <div class="divider-full"></div>

        <p class="section-label">Since you're already here, maybe try one of these:</p>

        <div class="available-pages">
          <a href="/" class="page-card">
            <span class="page-icon">📝</span>
            <span class="page-name">Posts</span>
            <span class="page-desc">Actual content. Revolutionary concept.</span>
          </a>
          <a href="/tags" class="page-card">
            <span class="page-icon">🏷️</span>
            <span class="page-name">Tags</span>
            <span class="page-desc">Organized chaos. At least it's organized.</span>
          </a>
          <a href="/about" class="page-card">
            <span class="page-icon">👤</span>
            <span class="page-name">About</span>
            <span class="page-desc">Who made this? Spoiler: Not You.</span>
          </a>
          <a href="/subscribe" class="page-card">
            <span class="page-icon">📬</span>
            <span class="page-name">Subscribe</span>
            <span class="page-desc">Get notified when real pages are added.</span>
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="divider"></div>

        <p class="footer-note">
          If you think this is a mistake, it probably is. But it's your mistake, not ours.
          <br/>
          You can <a href="mailto:sanket.maske@outlook.com">email me</a> about it.
          I may or may not respond, depending on the email content.
        </p>

      </div>
    </Layout>
  </body>
</html>

<style>
  .not-found {
    padding: 44px 0 60px;
    max-width: 640px;
  }

  .error-code {
    display: block;
    font-size: 7rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--text-color);
    letter-spacing: -0.05em;
    line-height: 1;
    opacity: 0.12;
    user-select: none;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
  }

  .error-title {
    display: block;
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--text-color);
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    line-height: 1.2;
    opacity: 0.6;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .divider-full {
    height: 5px;
    background: rgba(120, 130, 200, 0.4);
    border: none;
    margin: 1.5rem 0;
  }

  .divider {
    height: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(to right, rgba(120, 130, 200, 0.4), transparent);
    border: none;
    margin: 2rem 0;
  }

  .roast {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--text-color);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
  }

  .roast strong {
    color: var(--accent-color);
  }

  .excuse {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--accent-color);
    margin: 1.5rem 0;
    min-height: 1.4em;
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  .excuse:hover { opacity: 0.7; }

  .section-label {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: var(--second-text-color);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .available-pages {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(240px, 1fr));
    gap: 0.8rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .page-card {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.2rem;
    padding: 1rem 1.2rem;
    border: 1px dashed rgba(199,99,153,0.4);
    border-radius: 10px;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: background 0.15s, transform 0.15s;
  }

  .page-card:hover {
    background: rgba(199,99,153,0.06);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .page-icon { font-size: 1.2rem; }

  .page-name {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--accent-color);
  }

  .page-desc {
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    color: var(--second-text-color);
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .footer-note {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--second-text-color);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .footer-note a {
    color: var(--accent-color);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .footer-note a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
</style>
